(32, 1, '2018-03-30 07:40:37', '2018-03-30 11:40:37', 'We are a team of professionals to provide entire spectrum of financial products &amp; services available in Indian market according to the needs of our esteemed customers.\r\n\r\nWe cater all services in a smooth and professional way as a channel partner with leading banks, Insurance companies and non banking financial institutions. All the services are supported by our experience of 10Yrs in same field.\r\n\r\nOur experiences guide us to select and provide right product from right options as per satisfaction of customer. Since we respect customer satisfaction, we provide all financial services as per choice of customer, as we have all available options.\r\n\r\n<strong>Vision-</strong> To provide a single window for any financial services with customer satisfaction and better relationship.\r\n<h5><strong>Mission - Profit through:</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Better Services</li>\r\n 	<li>Quality</li>\r\n 	<li>Transparency</li>\r\n 	<li>Commitment</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h5><strong>In Simple words are known for:</strong></h5>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Expertise</li>\r\n 	<li>Customer Satisfaction</li>\r\n 	<li>Understanding of financial needs</li>\r\n 	<li>All services of different brands from a single window</li>\r\n</ul>', 'ABOUT US', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2018-05-30 08:12:07', '2018-05-30 12:12:07', '', 0, 'http://txdigital.ddns.net/dev/rim/wordpress/?page_id=32', 0, 'page', '', 0),
