(942, 1, '2018-05-24 01:15:18', '2018-05-24 05:15:18', 'Yes there is a rebate what is called deduction u/s 80-c on housing loan repayment upto Rs. 1.5 lakh in a year and a deduction on intt. payment of upto Rs. 2 lakh in a year . but that rebate or deduction can be claimed on a house property and not on plot or commercial property.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-medium wp-image-943 aligncenter\" src=\"http://txdigital.ddns.net/dev/rim/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/benefits-300x149.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"149\" />', 'Is there any rebate in income tax if i have availed a housing loan ?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'is-there-any-rebate-in-income-tax-if-i-have-availed-a-housing-loan', '', '', '2018-05-24 01:16:00', '2018-05-24 05:16:00', '', 0, 'http://txdigital.ddns.net/dev/rim/wordpress/?post_type=loan&#038;p=942', 0, 'loan', '', 0),
